      "message": "[🔴 Critical Issues] Line 51: The fallback timer clears the search filter but leaves `selectFirst_` set. If the original search result arrives after the timeout, or if clearing the filter itself emits `onSearchResultEnded()`, the adapter can select row 0 from the wrong result set/conversation. Reset the pending auto-selection before clearing the filter.\n```suggestion\nconnect(\u0026searchFallbackTimer_, \u0026QTimer::timeout, this, [this]() {\n    selectFirst_ \u003d false;\n    setFilter({});\n});\n```",
